Dear Junta,

The Art of Living Youth Club, IITM brings you a challenging as well as
enjoyable workshop, the "Happiness Program".

Workshop details:

This is a 15 hours workshop, which take you to the point where you
effortlessly reconnect to one inexhaustible source of joy  You. Once the
15 hours workshop is completed by the participant, they can attend
1.5 hours follow up session every week for a year.

Features:

Sudarshan Kriya, Yoga, Pranayama, Meditation, Group processes.

Sudarshan Kriya : Breathing is the first act of life. Within the breath
is the unexplored secret of life. Sudarshan Kriya is a powerful yet simple
rhythmic breathing technique that incorporates specific natural rhythms of
the breath, harmonizing the body, mind and emotions. The technique
eliminates stress, fatigue and negative emotions such as anger, frustration
and depression, leaving the mind calm, focused and the body energized,
completely relaxed.
To understand Sudarshan Kriya more scientifically, please go through the
article published in "International Journal of Yoga" in the following link:





Benefits of the program:

Stress free and Centered mind, Good Health, Heightened Enthusiasm, Enhanced
productivity and Efficiency.

Duration of the workshop : 15 hours

